			<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.authority-site.com/2011/08/app/appigo-todo-for-mac-is-good.html"><img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/todo-for-mac-top.jpg" alt="" title="todo-for-mac-top" width="521" height="246" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3639" /></a><br />
<span id="more-3630"></span></p>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
ぼくは Appigo の Todo シリーズがすっごく好きで愛用しています。<br />
iPhone でも iPad でも、便利でずっと使ってます。<br />
<a href="http://www.authority-site.com/2011/07/webservice/apple-days.html">Macbook Air</a> を買ったので、<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=J6rqkMpFl/4&#038;subid=&#038;offerid=94348.1&#038;type=10&#038;tmpid=3910&#038;RD_PARM1=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftodo%2Fid408975584%3Fmt%3D12">Todo for Mac</a> も使えるようになりました！<br />
ぼくが Appigo『<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=J6rqkMpFl/4&#038;subid=&#038;offerid=94348.1&#038;type=10&#038;tmpid=3910&#038;RD_PARM1=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftodo%2Fid408975584%3Fmt%3D12">Todo for Mac</a> 』を好きな理由を羅列していきます！
</p>
</div>
<h3>デザインが良い！</h3>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
ぼくは <a href="http://www.authority-site.com/2010/06/webservice/gtd-todo-toodledo.html">Toodledo</a> と同期して使っています。<br />
だったら Toodledo 使えばいいと思われるかもしれませんが、<br />
ぼくにとっては Web 版の Toodledo は使いにくいんです。
</p>
<p class="des2">
↓Toodledo (Web)<br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/bad-toodledo-web.jpg" alt="" title="bad-toodledo-web" width="450" height="277" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3641" />
</p>
<p class="des2">
↓<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=J6rqkMpFl/4&#038;subid=&#038;offerid=94348.1&#038;type=10&#038;tmpid=3910&#038;RD_PARM1=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftodo%2Fid408975584%3Fmt%3D12">Todo for Mac</a><br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/todo-for-mac-good-design.jpg" alt="todo-for-mac-good-design" title="todo-for-mac-good-design" width="400" height="395" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3644" />
</p>
</div>
<h3>GTD (Getting Things Done) 機能は万全！</h3>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
タグ、コンテキスト、受信箱 (inbox) 機能があります。<br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/todo-for-mac-function.jpg" alt="todo-for-mac-function" title="todo-for-mac-function" width="400" height="454" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3643" />
</p>
</div>
<h3>デバイス間でデザインの統一感がある！</h3>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
iPhone や iPad などの各デバイスごとの使いやすさを追求しながら、<br />
統一感も持たせてあるため、スムーズに移行できます。<br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/appigo-todo-iphone.jpg" alt="appigo-todo-iphone" title="appigo-todo-iphone" width="320" height="480" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3646" /><br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/appigo-todo-ipad.jpg" alt="appigo-todo-ipad" title="appigo-todo-ipad" width="500" height="375" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3645" /><br />
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/todo-for-mac-look.jpg" alt="todo-for-mac-look" title="todo-for-mac-look" width="368" height="500" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3647" />
</p>
</div>
<h3>カレンダーでタスクが把握できる！</h3>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
<img src="http://www.authority-site.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2011/08/todo-for-mac-easy.jpg" alt="" title="todo-for-mac-easy" width="400" height="454" class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3642" />
</p>
</div>
<div class="des2">
<p class="des2">
以上の理由で、Mac で GTD するなら『<a href="http://click.linksynergy.com/fs-bin/click?id=J6rqkMpFl/4&#038;subid=&#038;offerid=94348.1&#038;type=10&#038;tmpid=3910&#038;RD_PARM1=http%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fjp%2Fapp%2Ftodo%2Fid408975584%3Fmt%3D12">Todo for Mac</a>』が、オススメです。
</p>
